Package: rDTM
Title: R package retrieving data from IOM's DTM API
Version: 1.0.0.0000
Authors@R: 
    person("Xian", "Ji", , "xian.ji@un.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A easy way to retrieve data from IOM's DTM API in R.The DTM API shares data stored at the country, Admin 1 (states, provinces or equivalent) and Admin 2 (smaller subnational administrative areas) levels.(countryLevelData(), admin1LevelData(), admin2LevelData()).
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Depends: 
  R (>= 3.5.0),
  dplyr,
  httr,
  jsonlite
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
URL: https://github.com/jxaaa/rDTM
BugReports: https://github.com/jxaaa/rDTM/issues
